      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a dependable daily driver. While the car is mechanically sound and currently roadworthy, it has accumulated significant mileage and shows visible signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the clear coat is beginning to fade on the roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows typical wear and tear, including some minor stains on the upholstery and a worn steering wheel. The air conditioning and basic electronics are fully functional, though the vehicle will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
