      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic value! This reliable ride has plenty of life left and is perfect for anyone looking for dependable transportation on a budget. While it shows some honest wear and tear and minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with its age, it remains a solid and functional choice that's ready for its next owner!",
