      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of regular use. The exterior paint has some noticeable scratches on the rear bumper and a few small dings on the passenger doors, though there is no major body damage. Inside, the leather upholstery shows significant wear and creasing, particularly on the driver\u2019s seat, and the carpet has some staining in the footwells. Mechanically, the car starts and drives reliably, but the suspension is starting to feel soft and it will likely need new brake pads in the near future. All major electronics and the air conditioning system are fully functional. This is a dependable car for someone who prioritizes mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection.",
