      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies even the most discerning collector. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paint, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to excellence. Experience the pinnacle of pre-owned luxury, where mechanical integrity meets aesthetic perfection.",
