    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered coupe. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers peak torque with surgical precision through its six individual throttle bodies. This unit features a fully overhauled VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's critical points for long-term structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, short-throw engagement, channeling power to the rear wheels via the variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, offering the perfect balance of damping and rebound. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a paint depth consistent with factory application, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
