      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive care, presenting in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained by a single owner and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, the high-gloss trim is scratch-free, and the 'new car' aroma persists. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed strictly by master technicians using OEM parts. Every electronic component, safety sensor, and luxury amenity functions with precision. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade example that has been pampered since day one\u2014no accidents, no smoking, and no compromises. It drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it left the factory floor.",
